		<date>2015-02-06</date>
		<toc class="resources"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/OSI_model" title="Wikipedia: OSI Model">OSI</a></toc>
		<toc class="abstract">Layering is one of the fundamental abstractions of IT systems and models. As one way how the terms IoT and WoT can be defined and distinguished, it is possible to look at what the Internet and the Web are, how they are related, and how this can be translated into scenarios where resources are are real-world resources.</toc>
